hotel_text.important_information: This property does not accommodate bachelor(ette) or similar parties.

policies.content: You'll be charged 50% of the total price if you cancel your booking.

All children are welcome. Up to two children under 6 years stay free of charge when using existing beds.
Up to two children from 6 to 12 year are charged  VND 100000 per night when using existing beds.
Up to two children from 12 to 18 year are charged  VND 200000 per night when using existing beds.
One older child or adult is charged VND 200000  per night in an extra bed.
The maximum number of extra beds in a room is 1.
The maximum number of total guests in a room is 6.
There is no capacity for cribs in the room.
Any type of extra bed is upon request and needs to be confirmed by management.
Additional fees are not calculated automatically in the total cost and will have to be paid for separately during your stay.
WiFi is available in the hotel rooms and is free of charge.
Free public parking is available  at a location nearby (reservation is not needed).
Pets are not allowed.
You'll be charged a prepayment of 50% of the total price in the 14 days before arrival.
The property reserves the right to pre-authorize credit cards prior to arrival.
10 % VAT is included. A City tax is not applicable. A Service charge is not applicable.
